flowRoot.flowPara: Place foam marshmallows tightly spaced on the light gray wavy lines to form a road. Use Ozoblockly to get the Evo to the End.
+ Use the sensors to know which way to turn
+ Program the lights as "turn signals" when turning
+ When Evo sees Black color underneath, end the program and play the "Disco" lights and say the color at the finish.
+ If Evo runs into a barrier, update your program and try again!
Extra Credit: Increase the Evo's speed
Extra Credit: Add barriers inside the roadway
